<title>ḥbk kẖly̱ qlby ạ̉syr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- ḥbk kẖly̱ qlby ạ̉syr lsẖkẖṣk rby
 ạlqdyr
 yạlly bmwtk kẖdt mkạny wạ̹dytny bmwtk tḥryr
 2- bʿd mạ knt bʿyd wḍryr jytny wạ̉ṣbḥ qlby
 bṣyr
 nwrt ly ḥyạty wʿmry wṣnʿt fy qlby ạltgẖyyr</lyrics>
</song>